CRInfo

Shows supported cameras by the system

CRInfo contains samples of hundreds of raw files, each of them is made by a separate camera. Based on them, it checks which of them can be displayed by the system.

In order to be able to read the rawness of a given camera, you need the right codec for a particular camera model.

CRInfo warns which models are supported!


v1.0.0

Idle Clock Locker

Displays and locks the system idle clock

Idle Clock Locker falsely informs the system about user interaction - it does not interfere with the use of the computer, does not move the cursor or does not automatically press the keys.

For example: the messenger will not change its status to idle or the computer will not be turned off.

Lock your system idle clock!
